* ''Civilizing the Barbarian: A Critical Analysis of Behaviour Modification Programs in Forensic Psychiatric Settings''<ref>{{cite journal|last=Holmes|first=Dave|author2=Murray, Stuart J.|title=Civilizing the Barbarian: A Critical Analysis of Behaviour Modification Programs in Forensic Psychiatric Settings|journal=Journal of Nursing Management|year=2011|volume=19|issue=3|pages=293<U+2013>301|publisher=[[Wiley-Blackwell|Wiley]]|issn=1365-2834|doi=10.1111/j.1365-2834.2011.01207.x|pmid=21507099}}</ref>
* ''Entre soin et punition: la difficile coexistence entre le soin infirmier et la culture carc<U+00E9>rale''<ref>{{cite journal|last=Holmes|first=Dave|author2=Jacob, Jean-Daniel|title=Entre soin et punition: la difficile coexistence entre le soin infirmier et la culture carc<U+00E9>rale|journal=Recherche en soins infirmiers|year=2012|issue=111|pages=57<U+2013>66|url=http://www.bdsp.ehesp.fr/Base/462834/|issn=0297-2964|accessdate=3 January 2014}}</ref>
